Grilled mushroom, chicken, and papaya salad is a vibrant and nutritious dish that combines juicy grilled chicken with meaty portobello mushrooms, ripe papaya, and fresh greens. The combination of sweet and savoury flavours, along with the satisfying crunch of the greens and the tender texture of the chicken and mushrooms, make this salad a standout option for lunch or dinner. Recipe compliments of The South African Mushroom Farmersâ€™ Association. Dressing: For the dressing: For the chicken: 